Tamaziγt llan ghur-s tantaliwin tidiganin: 

* [[Tacelḥit]]
* [[Zayane|Tazayanit]]
* [[Tarifit]] (neγ '''Tamaziγt''', Tamaziγt Ugafa n Umerruk)
* [[Tacenwit]]
* [[Taqbaylit]] (neγ '''Tamaziγt''' / '''Tazwawt''') 
* [[Tacawit]]
* [[Tamashek]] (neγ Tatargit)

